name: pycosat
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}

package:
  name: pycosat
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pycosat-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pycosat/pycosat-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: c1fc35b17865f5f992595ae0362f9f9f

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pycosat

about:
  home: https://github.com/ContinuumIO/pycosat
  license: MIT
  summary: Bindings to picosat (a SAT solver)

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - kalefranz
    - mcg1969
    - msarahan
    - pelson
